    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIND YOUR WAY HOME, MASTER TIME </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A monkey, accidentally hurled into the future, now fights to return to the present and undo the chaos caused by the mad scientist, Dr. E. Will. Armed with time-manipulation powers, you'll battle through dystopian slums and sprawling cities, bending reality to outsmart mercenaries and overcome the obstacles in your way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198210/extras/27ddc9243ec637ef3ebd151d76a158f3.poster.avif?t=1737558003\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198210/extras/27ddc9243ec637ef3ebd151d76a158f3.webm?t=1737558003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198210/extras/27ddc9243ec637ef3ebd151d76a158f3.mp4?t=1737558003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEFEAT DR. E. WILL’S CREATIONS </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against relentless mercenaries and bizarre lab experiments engineered to stop you in your tracks. Use your time-manipulation powers to outmaneuver and outsmart your enemies. Get ready for speed, precision, and fast-paced combat, all while racing against the clock. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198210/extras/4c938d40464abe3150b9f9ac63fdac47.poster.avif?t=1737558003\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198210/extras/4c938d40464abe3150b9f9ac63fdac47.webm?t=1737558003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198210/extras/4c938d40464abe3150b9f9ac63fdac47.mp4?t=1737558003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SPEEDRUN YOUR WAY TO VICTORY </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For speedrunners and action fans alike, a timer tracks your every move. Set new personal bests, shatter developer-set records, and perfect your runs using the time-manipulation mechanic. The faster and more precise you are, the greater your rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198210/extras/9c80e9b653011a8f69e4f88e599b3b00.avif?t=1737558003\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198210/extras_big/9c80e9b653011a8f69e4f88e599b3b00.avif?t=1737558003 width=800 height=338 /></span></p>",
